      <title>匈牙利经济增速低于预期，逐步复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/hungary-s-economy-grows-less-than-forecast-in-gradual-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利第一季度经济增长低于预期，证实经济正在从经济衰退中缓慢复苏，而经济衰退给严峻的预算前景带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/hungary-s-economy-grows-less-than-forecast-in-gradual-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 06:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
